	VALUES ('tt0110413', 'L�on: The Professional', 'Mathilda, a 12-year-old girl, is reluctantly taken in by L�on, a professional assassin, after her family is murdered. L�on and Mathilda form an unusual relationship, as she becomes his prot�g�e and learns the assassin''s trade.', '[Jean Reno, Gary Oldman, Natalie Portman]', 'Luc Besson', '', '1994-11-18', '110 min', 667935, 8.6, 'After her father, mother and little brother are killed by her father''s employers, the 12-year-old daughter of an abject drug dealer is forced to take refuge in the apartment of a professional hitman who by her request, teaches her the methods of his job so she can take her revenge on the corrupt DEA agent who ruined her life by killing her beloved brother.', '[http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/small/unknown-1394846836._CB379391227_.png, http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/small/unknown-1394846836._CB379391227_.png, http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/small/unknown-1394846836._CB379391227_.png]', '[Crime, Drama, Thriller]', 64.0, 'assets/img/tt0110413.jpg', 1994);
