	VALUES ('tt0209144', 'Memento', 'A man creates a strange system to help him remember things; so he can hunt for the murderer of his wife without his short-term memory loss being an obstacle.', '[Guy Pearce, Carrie-Anne Moss, Joe Pantoliano]', 'Christopher Nolan', '', '2001-05-25', '113 min', 786269, 8.5, 'Memento chronicles two separate stories of Leonard, an ex-insurance investigator who can no longer build new memories, as he attempts to find the murderer of his wife, which is the last thing he remembers. One story line moves forward in time while the other tells the story backwards revealing more each time.', '[http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/small/unknown-1394846836._CB379391227_.png, http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/small/unknown-1394846836._CB379391227_.png]', '[Mystery, Thriller]', 80.0, 'assets/img/tt0209144.jpg', 2000);
