	VALUES ('tt0018455', 'Sunrise', 'A married farmer falls under the spell of a slatternly woman from the city, who tries to convince him to drown his wife.', '[George O''Brien, Janet Gaynor, Margaret Livingston]', 'F.W. Murnau', '', '1927-11-04', '94 min', 25568, 8.4, 'In this fable-morality subtitled "A Song of Two Humans", the "evil" temptress is a city woman who bewitches farmer Anses and tries to convince him to murder his neglected wife, Indre.', '[http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/small/unknown-1394846836._CB379391227_.png, http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/small/unknown-1394846836._CB379391227_.png, http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/small/unknown-1394846836._CB379391227_.png, http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/small/unknown-1394846836._CB379391227_.png, http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/small/unknown-1394846836._CB379391227_.png]', '[Comedy, Drama, Romance]', NULL, 'assets/img/tt0018455.jpg', 1927);
