	VALUES ('tt0083658', 'Blade Runner', 'A blade runner must pursue and try to terminate four replicants who stole a ship in space and have returned to Earth to find their creator.', '[Harrison Ford, Rutger Hauer, Sean Young]', 'Ridley Scott', '', '1982-06-25', '117 min', 431516, 8.2, 'In a cyberpunk vision of the future, man has developed the technology to create replicants, human clones used to serve in the colonies outside Earth but with fixed lifespans. In Los Angeles, 2019, Deckard is a Blade Runner, a cop who specializes in terminating replicants. Originally in retirement, he is forced to re-enter the force when four replicants escape from an off-world colony to Earth.', '[http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/small/unknown-1394846836._CB379391227_.png, http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/small/unknown-1394846836._CB379391227_.png, http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/small/unknown-1394846836._CB379391227_.png]', '[Sci-Fi, Thriller]', 88.0, 'assets/img/tt0083658.jpg', 1982);
