	VALUES ('tt0060827', 'Persona', 'A nurse is put in charge of an actress who can''t talk and finds that the actress''s persona is melding with hers.', '[Bibi Andersson, Liv Ullmann, Margaretha Krook]', 'Ingmar Bergman', '', '1967-03-16', '83 min', 55664, 8.2, 'A young nurse, Alma, is put in charge of Elisabeth Vogler: an actress who is seemingly healthy in all respects, but will not talk. As they spend time together, Alma speaks to Elisabeth constantly, never receiving any answer. Alma eventually confesses her secrets to a seemingly sympathetic Elisabeth and finds that her own personality is being submerged into Elisabeth''s persona.', '[http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/small/unknown-1394846836._CB379391227_.png, http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/small/unknown-1394846836._CB379391227_.png, http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/small/unknown-1394846836._CB379391227_.png, http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/small/unknown-1394846836._CB379391227_.png]', '[Drama, Thriller]', NULL, 'assets/img/tt0060827.jpg', 1966);
