	VALUES ('tt2015381', 'Guardians of the Galaxy', 'A group of intergalactic criminals are forced to work together to stop a fanatical warrior from taking control of the universe.', '[Chris Pratt, Vin Diesel, Bradley Cooper]', 'James Gunn', '', '2014-08-01', '121 min', 581306, 8.1, 'After stealing a mysterious orb in the far reaches of outer space, Peter Quill from Earth, is now the main target of a manhunt led by the villain known as Ronan the Accuser. To help fight Ronan and his team and save the galaxy from his power, Quill creates a team of space heroes known as the "Guardians of the Galaxy" to save the world.', '[http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/small/unknown-1394846836._CB379391227_.png, http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/small/unknown-1394846836._CB379391227_.png, http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/G/01/imdb/images/nopicture/small/unknown-1394846836._CB379391227_.png]', '[Action, Adventure, Sci-Fi]', 76.0, 'assets/img/tt2015381.jpg', 2014);
